title: Maestro Error.
body: Yes, I have tried running as a administrator, and many other methods. None have worked. {{item:3070}}

replies.body: I'd like to help you out here, but I could use some more information.  Where exactly are you seeing this maestro error?  For example, is it while trying to login, load the patcher, or something else?  Anything can help, so let me know!
It just seems to be a certain time after I log in and get into queue, but I have not tried waiting on the login screen.
